        "description": {
            "value": "<p>When you hit a creature with a weapon attack, you can expend one superiority die to attempt to disarm the target, forcing it to drop one item of your choice that it&rsquo;s holding. You add the superiority die to the attack&rsquo;s damage roll, and the target must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, it drops the object you choose. The object lands at its feet.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>To support full damage on save in midi-qoi set <strong>Check Spell Text</strong>&nbsp;to true, otherwise the save will apply to the damage as well as the effect.</p>\n</section>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
